<p>185. The Special Rapporteur regrets that the Government of Yemen failed to respond to 
the communication dated 19 October 2011, thereby withholding cooperation with the 
mandate established by the Human Rights Council. The communication referred to the </p>

<p><b>A/HRC/19/61/Add.4 
</b></p>
<p><b>80</b>  
</p>
<p>alleged incommunicado detention and deterioration of health condition of Mr. Al-Sharafy, a 
human rights activist. In this connection, the Special Rapporteur would like to draw the 
